<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
  <title>CSS Reftest Reference</title>
  <link rel="author" title="Hajime Shiozawa" href="mailto:hajime.shiozawa@gmail.com" />
  <style type="text/css"><![CDATA[
    div#outer
    {
      padding-right: 0.3em; /* 1.5em * 0.2 */
      width: 1.2em; /* 1.5em * 0.8 */
      font: 3.75em/1.5 Ahem; /* computes to 60px/90px */
    }

    div#small
    {
      float: right;
      background-color: fuchsia;
      height: 0.5em;
      width: 0.4em; /* 0.5em * 0.8 */
    }
    div#big
    {
      float: right;
      background-color: fuchsia;
      height: 1.5em;
      width: 1.2em; /* 1.5em * 0.8 */
    }

    div#normal
    {
      float: right;
      background-color: fuchsia;
      height: 1em;
      width: 0.8em; /* 1em * 0.8 */
    }
    ]]></style>

  </head>

  <body>

  <p>Test passes if there is a pink polygon and if its right vertical edge is straight, uniform and unbroken.</p>

  <div id="outer"><div id="small"></div><div id="big"></div><div id="normal"></div></div>

  </body>
</html>
